title: Homemade dog food sardine and liver meal
ingredients: ['2 sardines', '2 tablespoons chopped fresh spinach', '1 tablespoon finely chopped apple (no pips)', '2 tablespoons chopped organic grass fed beef liver', '1/4 teaspoon human grade bone meal', '1/4 teaspoon organic dried kelp', '1 tablespoon finely chopped carrot', '1/2 teaspoon fish oil', '1/2 teaspoon liquid K-9 glucosamine']
